text:
DBS ATM at ARC, is still here, but they've reconsolidated their space towards the other side of the mall. 2nd floor, right by the escalator.

With all the automation happening, what's left of DBS is but a small portion, that services the core needs, including how you're probably also not needing as much cash as you needed before.
On the second floor, you can deposit cheque at anytime. Just put it into the deposit box
